Bangladesh to Buy 50,000 Tons of Rice From Phoenix Commodities

-- B y   A r u n   D e v n a t h
-- 
2011-06-19T13:17:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-19/bangladesh-to-buy-50-000-tons-of-rice-from-phoenix-commodities.html
Bangladesh will buy 50,000 metric
tons of non-basmati parboiled rice from Phoenix Commodities
Pvt., a British Virgin Islands-based company, after a cabinet
committee approved the purchase, Nurul Karim, joint secretary of
the Cabinet Division, said.  Phoenix quoted $509 per ton of rice, making it the first
lowest bidder among eight participants, Karim said by phone
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Arun Devnath in Mumbai at 
